parameters:
Noble Perosu: I have heard that you are the heroes who have
liberated the village of Rippi. Thank you for coming.

Noble Perosu: There are only a few survivors left in the
village of Rippi... Allow me to express my gratitude in
their place.

Clea: I apologize, please tell us the details of the
request.

Noble Perosu: You should know about the underground cave. It
used to be a place where devil worshippers lived in hiding.

Noble Perosu: Now it has become the dwelling of hideous
monsters. The request is to exterminate the monsters and
retrieve the corpses of four beings.
Clea: Understood, we will definitely accomplish it.

Noble Perosu: The monsters have an abnormal attachment to
the corpses, so please be careful as they may attack during
the retrieval.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Noble Perno: The remains should be buried with care. Please,
also for the sake of relieving their regrets.

Noble Perosu: Indeed, those who have been recognized by the
priestess of Actina for the recovery of corpses and the
subjugation of monsters.

Noble Perosu: We will further seal the deepest part of the
underground cave. We have already contacted the Terios
Church and the Magic Academy--

Noble Perosu: If we spread rumors, this will be our reward
for this time.

Priestess Sophia: May I assist with the sealing? I have
quite a connection with this place.

Mage Relm: Please count me in as well. It would be more
efficient to have a genius like me!

Noble Perosu: You couldn't ask for more! We will give you an
additional reward, so please, I beg you.
Clea: Is there anything we can do as well?

Noble Perosu: The entire village is quite damaged and we
need to bring in a lot of materials...

Thief Nora: Leave it to me! I'm really good at simple
physical work!

Noble Perosu: Um, so next is... cleaning up this place, I
suppose.

Clea: I apologize for causing you trouble by being
considerate.

Noble Perosu: We temporarily moved the belongings from other
buildings.

Noble Perosu: While it is certainly sinful to use valuable
heirlooms, we will allocate them towards the reconstruction
expenses.
Clea: In that case, it might be better not to work in armor.
Clea: Please wait for just a moment.
Clea: It seems like there won't be any problems with this.
Noble Perosu: No, let's continue with the work.
Clea: What should we do next?

Noble Perosu: Yes, that's right. Can you please help me move
that wooden box over there?
Clea: This is it, heave ho--

Noble Perosu: This is an extremely valuable plate. It can be
said to be the most expensive item in this village.

Noble Perosu: Ahaha, it was just a joke. You're so beautiful
that I couldn't resist playing a prank.
Noble Perosu: Um... Are you okay?

Noble Perosu: Haha, so you were in the mood for it!
Although, I've been in the mood since I first saw you.
Noble Perosu: Hehehe, please come over here, Master.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
Noble Perosu: Thank you so much for everything.
Noble Perosu: This will be an additional reward.

Noble Perosu: I think it will take time for the village to
recover. Please come and visit once the residents have
settled in.

Noble Perosu: ...We are always recruiting maids, so feel
free to apply anytime.
Clea: Please stop with the jokes, then.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Noble Perno: The reconstruction will take time. Please
continue to support us and take breaks when needed...

Noble Perno: The reconstruction of this village is a
lifelong mission for me.
Do you want to skip the adult scene?

Noble Perosu: As always, the maid outfit suits you. It makes
me feel like a real master...
Noble Perosu: Now, I must discipline this clumsy maid.
